籤詩版本二:
Makemake au e hoʻowalewale i ka Gui Make ʻole i loko o ka Hale Aliʻi Toad, akā e wehe wau i ka puka o ka lani a hoʻokuʻu iā ʻoe.
ʻAʻole nō, maikaʻi ka nūhou, ʻakaʻaka nā mea a pau i nā pua ma ka piko o ke kuahiwi
詩意:
Aia kēia hexagram i ka hōʻailona o ka osmanthus make ʻole.
Pono nā kānaka hanohano ma nā mea a pau.
解曰: ʻO ka makemake o nā mea kālepa. Aia (ʻaʻole) pilikia i ke komo ʻana. Ua hoʻoholo ʻia ka maʻi a ua hoʻoholo ʻia ka hoʻopiʻi. E hana i nā mea āu e hiki ai.
籤詩故事一:
◇ E lokomaikaʻi a noʻonoʻo
Ua hānau ʻia ʻo Gao Huaide (926-982), ka inoa aloha ʻo Zangyong, ma Changshan, Zhending (ʻo Zhengding, Hebei i kēia manawa).
I ka wā o "Chenqiao Mutiny", no ka mea, ua kākoʻo ʻo Gao Huaide iā Zhao Kuangyin ma ke ʻano he Emepera, ua hoʻokiʻekiʻe ʻia ʻo ia i hope luna nui i mua o ka hale aliʻi.
Ua mare pū ʻo Gao Huaide i ke kaikuahine o Song Taizu Zhao Kuangyin (ʻelua kaikuahine ʻo Zhao Kuangyin, ua make kekahi i ka wā ʻōpiopio a ua kapa ʻia ʻo Princess Chen ma hope o kona make ʻana; ua male kekahi iā Miford, akā naʻe, ua make kāna kāne a he wahine kāne make ʻo ia, no laila ʻo Zhao Kuangyin. Ua kapa ʻia ʻo ia ʻo ke kaikamahine mua o Yan). ʻO ka inoa kūhelu ʻo Prince Consort Duwei.
(ʻOiai he kanaka hoʻokumu a male i ke kaikuahine o ka mōʻī, ʻaʻohe pono e hopohopo no ka loaʻa ʻole o kahi kūlana kūlana.)
聖意: Haaheo ka hale, pomaikai ka imi waiwai, pilikia ka oihana, pilikia ka mare, pilikia o Liujia, pilikia na enuhe silika, maikai ole ke kula, pilikia na enuhe silika, pilikia na holoholona eono. maikaʻi ʻole, paʻakikī ka loaʻa ʻana o ka poʻe, ʻo ka hoʻopiʻi lehulehu i ka haʻaheo, ʻaʻole pōmaikaʻi ka neʻe ʻana, nalowale waiwai, maʻi, Anshan, kupapaʻu, kahiko auspiciousness
第X籤: He iwakāluakūmākolu i lanakila i ka hailona
